    { "_comment": "── Single-utterance stroke corrections (\"make it a six instead\", \"actually six\", \"scratch that, six\"). The parser flags these with `correction: true` so the call site overwrites the most recent entry rather than appending a new one. ──", "_groupKey": "singleUtteranceCorrection",
